h1 Course View - #{ course.name }

- if ( subscribed )
	a( href = '/course/#{ course._id }/unsubscribe' ) Unsubscribe from this course
- else
	a( href = '/course/#{ course._id }/subscribe' ) Subscribe to this course

p Lectures

ul
	- each lecture in lectures
		li
			a( href = '/lecture/#{ lecture._id }' ) #{ lecture.name }

a( href = '/course/#{ course._id }/lecture/new' ) New Lecture
